nch to check for growth. Scales with transcript size.\\n\\n3. **Session state file I/O — ~1-2ms/session**. `store.List()` reads + JSON-parses every `.json` file in `.git/entire-sessions/`.\\n\\n4. **Tree traversal — ~1-2ms/session**. go-git's `tree.File()` walks subtree objects to find the transcript.\\n\\n5. **Content overlap checks — ~3-5ms/session (conditional)**. Comparing staged/committed files against `FilesTouched` requires reading tree entries.\\n\\nThe highest-ROI optimizations would be batch ref resolution (load all refs once into a map) and caching the shadow ref across `listAllSessionStates()` → `filterSessionsWithNewContent()`.\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":323,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":91843,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":323},\"output_tokens\":2,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYZBKHmRY8yfbUVSbizKv\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"84f145b2-ba6d-4089-9585-0bf0fbf5eef7\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-27T20:08:36.786Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"84f145b2-ba6d-4089-9585-0bf0fbf5eef7\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/evisdrenova/code/entire/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"2b47f0e1-cbe2-4531-8916-a2cd4d2d944d\",\"version\":\"2.1.56\",\"gitBranch\":\"sessionPruning\",\"slug\":\"clever-leaping-stream\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"type\":\"hook_progress\",\"hookEvent\":\"Stop\",\"hookName\":\"Stop\",\"command\":\"go run ${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/cmd/entire/main.go hooks claude-code stop\"},\"parentToolUseID\":\"26f97b18-1f04-4ec5-86d2-68ffefc8a8f0\",\"toolUseID\":\"26f97b18-1f04-4ec5-86d2-68ffefc8a8f0\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-27T20:08:36.851Z\",\"uuid\":\"58779ca3-7846-4a6a-8a23-26ac67988d0b\"}\n"